-- Buffett Tells Fox Business He Supports Fed Work During Crisis
-- B y   D a n   R e i c h l
-- 2012-05-03T23:58:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-03/buffett-tells-fox-business-he-supports-fed-work-during-crisis.html
Warren Buffett, chairman and chief
executive officer of  Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A) , said the U.S.
Federal Reserve made the right moves in combating the 2008
credit crisis and ensuing recession.  The central bank “did the right thing,” Buffett, 81, said
on the Fox Business channel in an interview broadcast today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
